title: Rai Muhammad Murtaza Iqbal wins PP-203 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Rai Muhammad Murtaza Iqbal, an independent candidate, has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-203 Sahiwal-VI by securing 55,874 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Muhammad Hanif of Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz (PML-N) who bagged 35,163 votes.
Votersâ€™ turnout remained 54.03 %.
